name: Sarah Snook
description:
Sarah Snook is an Australian actress, mainly known for her role as Shiv Roy in the HBO series Succession.

1850-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings. (Reduced learning rate to 0.002 after step 1000.)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
This is step 1500. I'll probably upload step 1000 as version 1.0 later on, as I think it also offers very good results and I'm a bit undecided as to which is the best one. I will keep training the model and, in case I still manage to find a better version, I'll also upload that one.

Note: In the end, I decided to discard step 1000 and I uploaded step 1850 instead (as version 1.5), since it was the one that I liked the most out of the several versions I tested.
